	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod proxime de transitu <placeName type="auto_name">Gonzagae</placeName> permisso scripsi, ea conditione interea factum intellexi, ut sine omni armatura bellioque apparatu, si velit, transeat, id quod cum ipse nolit, alia via exercitum deducet in Inferiorem Germaniam, per vallem scilicet Athesinam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepimus quoque interea ex <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> literas, quibus significatur <persName type="auto_name">Ioannem Friderychum</persName>, Saxonię ducem 3. martii e vivis excessisse simulque 9 diebus ante ipsum obiisse uxorem suam.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Obiit quoque <persName ref="p17810" cert="high">Arnoldus</persName> ille, ducis <persName ref="p8105" cert="high">Ottonis Heinrychi</persName> quaestor, quem nosti.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alias ex <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> nihil habemus, nisi quod de comitiis a Caesare indictis scribunt, quae tamen non futura sperant.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es sol <persName type="auto_name">hertzog Christoff von Wirtenberg</persName> imm anfang diß monats ußgezogen sin für <placeName ref="l1426" cert="high">Hohen-Rechberg</placeName>, das schloß, von wegen das imm derselbig edelman, <persName type="auto_name">Uͦtz von Rechberg</persName> genannt, zwen puren erstochen.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Die <placeName type="auto_name">Nürenbergischen</placeName> söllend auch noch vor <placeName type="auto_name">Blasenburg</placeName> ligen, <placeName type="auto_name">Ruchenpalm</placeName> eroberet haben, deß kriegens muͤd sin und deß marggrafen halb in großen sorgen ston.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zuͦ <placeName ref="l513" cert="high">Ulm</placeName> hatt man wider ein predicanten, der gar lutherisch, und halt man in einer kirchen 3 religiones nacheinander.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Diß schript <persName type="auto_name">Onoffrius Hürus</persName> Blaurero, der selb da gwesen.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Idem de <placeName type="auto_name">Anglia</placeName> multa et plausibilia, sed non admodum certa.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribit <persName type="auto_name">Schertlinum</persName> Caesari quidem reconciliatum, nondum vero <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinando</persName> regi, id quod diversum est ab eo, quid hic de illo fuit sparsum; <foreign xml:lang="de">hatt ein predicanten widerumb gen <placeName ref="l76" cert="high">Burtenbach</placeName>, da sin herrschafft ist, gesetzt.</foreign></s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec quoniam ex <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> partim, partim a Blaurero accepimus, volui tibi quoque communicare, quamvis haec ipsa et multa alia et certiora te habere existimem.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hodie lecti sunt senatores novi 3, inter quos <persName type="auto_name">Wolphgangus ab Erlach</persName> fratri <persName type="auto_name">Ioanni Rodolpho</persName> successit, quem etiam (non dubito) prudentia superabit, humanitate certe nunc antecellit longe.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutat te quęstor <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerus</persName>, <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName> noster et <persName type="auto_name">Schlatterus</persName>, simul quoque uxor mea; salvi sint omnes tui.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName> 28. martii.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fratri meo nihil scribo; salutabis illum ex me et ex his, quę videbuntur, poteris communicare.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. Heinrycho Bullingero, Tigurinae ecclesiae fidelissimo pastori, domino et compatri suo charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zürich.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">M. Heinrych Bullingeren.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
